thread.title: Thing Json import

comments.text: Hi! As of v153.3 (you're on [version]), you can press Ctrl+V on the main dialog (the one with the "Create Thing" button) to import a custom JSON thing definition!
Pls note this is not custom 3D model importing, but importing of something base-shapes based that you could also manually create.
This allows e.g. external tools constructing the thing. Hope you enjoy!
